01. create the folder to store the project
02. open terminal in there and type 
    "flutter create project_name"

03.open project in VS code application
04. open 'lib/main.dart' file
05. install 'flutter'  extension for VS code
06. connect any device 
07. run 'flutter doctor'



create a flutter project in VS Code

01. open VS Code
02. Press [ Ctrl + P ]
03. type '>' sybol on the comming text area
04. select 'flutter new project' option in the drop down list
05. asign aname for the project
06. select saving file location
